# TTB Label Checker - Frontend Environment Variables
# ===================================================

# Cloud Functions API Endpoint
# -----------------------------
# For local development with Firebase emulator (uncomment to use):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5001/ttb-label-checker/us-east4

# API Endpoint
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://us-east4-ttb-label-checker.cloudfunctions.net

# Notes:
# - This is the ONLY environment variable needed for the frontend
# - No Firebase API key needed (we use plain HTTP fetch, not Firebase SDK)
# - The region (us-east4) matches the backend deployment in functions/main.py
# - Make sure to run `firebase emulators:start` before local testing
